Class DeviceManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • DeviceManager

  • public class DeviceManager
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that acts as all the devices the GUI has to utilize to change the values for the currents. It contains setter and getter methods for its instance variables The devices include: AC, Furnace, Sprinkler, Humidifier
